        sy += y
        sz += z
        svx += vx
        svy += vy

        tmin = 0

            tmin = 0
        else:
            dmin = sqrt((time * svx + sx) ** 2 + (time * svy + sy) ** 2 + (time * svz + sz) ** 2) / float(n)
            tmin = time
    return (dmin, tmin)
